developer_response.body:
To cope with nausea, please consider the following:
- Adjust "Dynamic Comfort mode" bar in the settings and set it to the max; 
- In our experience, motion sickness ceases to be a problem relatively quickly if you give yourself and the game a chance;
- During the adjustment period - try to limit your gaming sessions in VR. Make them shorter, even if more frequent than usual;
- It has been proved that chewing gum reduces visually induced motion sickness: https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00221-021-06303-5
- Try playing with a fan facing you in the same room as you play.
